g/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/90 flex-1\">Incredible work! The developer set up our entire e-commerce platform from scratch. From design to payment integration to shipping, everything works perfectly. Technical skills are top-notch and very easy to work with.</p><div class=\"space-y-1.5\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs\"><span class=\"w-20 text-muted-foreground shrink-0\">Communication</span><div class=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-muted rounded-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\" style=\"width:100%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-6 text-right font-medium\">5</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs\"><span class=\"w-20 text-muted-foreground shrink-0\">Quality of Work</span><div class=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-muted rounded-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\" style=\"width:100%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-6 text-right font-medium\">5</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs\"><span class=\"w-20 text-muted-foreground shrink-0\">Timeliness</span><div class=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-muted rounded-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\" style=\"width:80%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-6 text-right font-medium\">4</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs\"><span class=\"w-20 text-muted-foreground shrink-0\">Value for Money</span><div class=\"flex-1 h-1.5 bg-muted rounded-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full bg-emerald-500 rounded-full\" style=\"width:100%\"></div></div><span class=\"w-6 text-right font-medium\">5</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between pt-1\"><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs transition-colors text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-thumbs-up h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 10v12\"></path><path d=\"M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z\"></path></svg>Helpful (<!-- -->42<!-- -->)</button></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 p-3 mt-1\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-semibold text-emerald-700 mb-1 flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z\"></path></svg>Seller responded:</p><p class=\"text-xs text-emerald-800 leading-relaxed\">Michael, it was an absolute joy working on your e-commerce project! Your clear requirements made my job much easier. I&#x27;m thrilled the platform is performing well. Let me know if you need any enhancements!</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span data-slot=\"avatar\" class=\"relative flex size-8 overflow-hidden rounded-full h-10 w-10 shrink-0\"><span data-slot=\"avatar-fallback\" class=\"flex size-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-400 to-pink-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold\">LA</span></span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\"><span class=\"f